OL,3,CMotorcyclist in serious condition
OL,4,Cafter crashing into van
OL,6,FA motorcyclist remains in a serious
OL,7,Fcondition following a crash with a van
OL,8,Fon the Lisnevenagh Road in Ballymena
OL,9,Fon Saturday.
OL,11,FThe Air Ambulance was dispatched to
OL,12,Fthe scene along with police and the
OL,13,Fambulance service and the injured man
OL,14,Fwas taken to hospital.
OL,16,FThe PSNI said the van driver was
OL,17,Funinjured in the collision.
OL,19,FOfficers are appealing to anyone with
OL,20,Finformation or dash cam footage of the
OL,21,Fincident to contact them.
